  </div></section>
); })}

<!-- §5 SECTORS -->
<section class="dsec" id="sectors"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="sec-head"><div><div class="eyebrow">§5 · Where is leadership, and does it fit the cycle?</div><h2>Sector rotation &amp; the business cycle.</h2></div><span class="fresh-tag">structural + daily RS</span></div>
  <p class="lead">The <b>durable</b> sensitivity map — what each sector is structurally driven by. Click a column to sort. Live relative-strength and the cycle clock are feed-pending; the conflict winner/loser is the <i>overlay</i> in §Catalysts.</p>
  <div style="overflow-x:auto"><table class="dtbl" id="sectbl">
    <thead><tr><th>Sector</th><th class="sort" data-col="cyc">Cycle</th><th class="sort" data-col="rate">Rates</th><th class="sort" data-col="oil">Oil</th><th>ETF</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>{sectors.map((r, i) => (<tr data-cyc={r.cyc[1]} data-rate={r.rate[1]} data-oil={r.oil[1]}><td class="nm">{r.s}</td><td class="sens">{r.cyc[0]}</td><td class={`sens ${r.rate[2]}`}>{r.rate[0]}</td><td class={`sens ${r.oil[2]}`}>{r.oil[0]}</td><td class="mono">{sectorProfiles[i] ? sectorProfiles[i].etf : ''}</td></tr>))}</tbody>
  </table></div>
  <figure class="snap-chart clock" style="margin-top:14px"><div class="cp-h"><b>Business-cycle clock — where leadership sits</b><span class="cp-tag">illustrative</span></div>
    <div class="sc-svg"><svg viewBox="0 0 320 150" role="img" aria-label="Illustrative business-cycle clock with early, mid, late and recession quadrants">
      <circle cx="160" cy="78" r="62" fill="none" stroke="var(--cardline)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <line x1="160" y1="16" x2="160" y2="140" stroke="var(--cardline)" stroke-width="1"/><line x1="98" y1="78" x2="222" y2="78" stroke="var(--cardline)" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="176" y="44" fill="var(--struct)" font-size="9" font-family="Lora,serif">Early — Cyclicals</text>
      <text x="176" y="116" fill="var(--muted)" font-size="9" font-family="Lora,serif">Late — Energy/Mat</text>
      <text x="60" y="116" fill="var(--neg)" font-size="9" font-family="Lora,serif" text-anchor="end">Recession — Defensives</text>
      <text x="60" y="44" fill="var(--muted)" font-size="9" font-family="Lora,serif" text-anchor="end">Mid — Tech/Inds</text>
      <line x1="160" y1="78" x2="206" y2="50" stroke="var(--eyeb)" stroke-width="2.5"/><circle cx="160" cy="78" r="4" fill="var(--eyeb)"/>
    </svg></div>
  </figure>
  <div class="deep">
